                                                    <a href="javascript: expand(document.getElementById('answer467'));">
                                                      Leagues                                                    </a>
                                                  </div>
                                                  <div id="answer467" style="padding:5px; display:none;">
                                                    <div><b>Request</b><br>To tell the API that this is a request for league information:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;r=l</pre></div><br>(Lower case "L")<br><br><b>Additional Request Data</b><br>At least one of the following is required:<br><br>To retrieve an individual league:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;leagueid=[LEAGUE_ID]</pre></div><br><br>To retrieve multiple leagues:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;leagueids=[LEAGUE_ID],[LEAGUE_ID],...</pre></div><br><br>To retrieve a leagueid based on the season, country, division, and league:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;season=[SEASON]&amp;country_iso=[COUNTRY_ISO]&amp;division=[DIVISION]
  &amp;league=[LEAGUE]</pre></div><br><br>To retrieve all leagues in a division based on the season, country, and division:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;season=[SEASON]&amp;country_iso=[COUNTRY_ISO]&amp;division=[DIVISION]</pre></div><br><br>To retrieve all leagues in a division based on the division ID:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;divisionid=[DIVISION_ID]</pre></div><br><br>If any league is not found, no information will be returned for that fixture, not even an empty league element.<br><br><b>Response</b><br><br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&lt;league id="6"&gt;
  &lt;id&gt;6&lt;/id&gt;
  &lt;country_iso&gt;NZ&lt;/country_iso&gt;
  &lt;season&gt;1&lt;/season&gt;
  &lt;division&gt;3&lt;/division&gt;
  &lt;league&gt;1&lt;/league&gt;
  &lt;lounge&gt;116&lt;/lounge&gt;
&lt;/league&gt;</pre></div><br><br><b>Notes:</b><br><br><b>Lounge</b> This is the lounge ID of the league's clubrooms lounge.</div>                                                  </div>
                                                </div>
                                                                                            
