                                                  </div>
                                                  <div id="answer485" style="padding:5px; display:none;">
                                                    <div><b>Request</b><br>To tell the API that this is a request for mail:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;r=ma</pre></div><br><br><b>Additional Request Data</b><br><br>To retrieve message summaries and subfolder information. where FOLDER_ID is 1,2,3,4 for Inbox,Sent,Deleted,Saved:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;folderid=[FOLDER_ID],[FOLDER_ID],...</pre></div><br><br>To retrieve message summaries of messages in a subfolder:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;subfolderid=[SUBFOLDER_ID],[SUBFOLDER_ID],...</pre></div><br><br>To retrieve an individual message:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;messageid=[MESSAGE_ID]</pre></div><br><br>If no additional request data is given the default is <span style="font-size:140%; vertical-align: middle; margin: -25% 0;">“</span>&amp;folderid=1,2,3,4<span style="font-size:140%; vertical-align: middle; margin: -25% 0;">”</span><br><br><b>Response (Top level folder, e.g. Inbox)</b><br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&lt;folderid&gt; 
