                                                    <a href="javascript: expand(document.getElementById('answer483'));">
                                                      Match Commentary                                                    </a>
                                                  </div>
                                                  <div id="answer483" style="padding:5px; display:none;">
                                                    <div><b>Request</b><br>To tell the API that this is a request for match commentary:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;r=me</pre></div><br><br><b>Additional Request Data</b><br><br>A single fixture ID must be provided:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;fixtureid=[FIXTURE_ID]</pre></div><br><br>To specify a youth match:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;youth=1</pre></div><br><br>To specify an International match:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;nat=1</pre></div><br><br>To specify an Under 20 match:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;u20=1</pre></div><br><br>If the match is not found, or the match hasn't run yet, or the match data has since been removed. You will receive the applicable error message.<br><br><b>Response</b><br><br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&lt;event&gt;
  &lt;id&gt;220653&lt;/id&gt;
  &lt;fixtureid&gt;4923654&lt;/fixtureid&gt;
  &lt;commentary&gt;Blackout Rugby Stadium is filled to the rafters with chanting, stamping fans. The [team id=2]Chiefs[/team] won't lack for support today! [player id=9447603]Younger[/player] is looking at the ref. Here we are, the big game is ON!&lt;/commentary&gt;
  &lt;possession&gt;1&lt;/possession&gt;
  &lt;actualtime&gt;1&lt;/actualtime&gt;
  &lt;losttime&gt;0&lt;/losttime&gt;
  &lt;gametime&gt;1&lt;/gametime&gt;
  &lt;homescore&gt;0&lt;/homescore&gt;
  &lt;guestscore&gt;0&lt;/guestscore&gt;
  &lt;index&gt;1&lt;/index&gt;
  &lt;half&gt;1&lt;/half&gt;
&lt;/event&gt;
&lt;event&gt;
  &lt;id&gt;220654&lt;/id&gt;
  &lt;fixtureid&gt;4923654&lt;/fixtureid&gt;
  &lt;commentary&gt;That's an a mid-length kick out to left field by [player id=9447603]Younger[/player]. [player id=3686163]Ripper[/player] is under it for the [team id=2]Chiefs[/team], but there's a stampede of opposition forwards coming his way!&lt;/commentary&gt;
  &lt;possession&gt;0&lt;/possession&gt;
  &lt;actualtime&gt;7&lt;/actualtime&gt;
  &lt;losttime&gt;0&lt;/losttime&gt;
  &lt;gametime&gt;7&lt;/gametime&gt;
  &lt;homescore&gt;0&lt;/homescore&gt;
  &lt;guestscore&gt;0&lt;/guestscore&gt;
  &lt;index&gt;2&lt;/index&gt;
  &lt;half&gt;1&lt;/half&gt;
&lt;/event&gt;
&lt;event&gt;
  &lt;id&gt;220655&lt;/id&gt;
  &lt;fixtureid&gt;4923654&lt;/fixtureid&gt;
  &lt;commentary&gt;It's wet out here and [player id=3686163]Ripper[/player] knows it. That ball was like a bar of soap in a prison - nobody wanted to pick it up. Knock-on.&lt;/commentary&gt;
  &lt;possession&gt;1&lt;/possession&gt;
  &lt;actualtime&gt;10&lt;/actualtime&gt;
  &lt;losttime&gt;0&lt;/losttime&gt;
  &lt;gametime&gt;10&lt;/gametime&gt;
  &lt;homescore&gt;0&lt;/homescore&gt;
  &lt;guestscore&gt;0&lt;/guestscore&gt;
  &lt;index&gt;3&lt;/index&gt;
  &lt;half&gt;1&lt;/half&gt;
&lt;/event&gt;</pre></div><br><br><b>Notes:</b><br><br><b>Tags</b> You will need to parse the commentary for team and player tags.<br><br><b>New Paragraphs</b> If the commentary field is empty, this signifies a new paragraph.<br><br><b>Actual Time</b> Number of actual seconds passed since the start of the match, including half time, lost time, etc.<br><br><b>Game Time</b> Number of seconds on the game clock. Starts at 0 in the first half, and 40x60 in the second half.<br><br><b>Lost Time</b> The amount of time lost due to injury, or video review, etc.</div>                                                  </div>
