                                                  <div>
                                                    <a href="javascript: expand(document.getElementById('answer484'));">
                                                      Match Score                                                    </a>
                                                  </div>
                                                  <div id="answer484" style="padding:5px; display:none;">
                                                    <div><b>Request</b><br>To tell the API that this is a request for live scoring information:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;r=ls</pre></div><br><br><b>Additional Request Data</b><br><br>A single fixture ID must be provided:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;fixtureid=[FIXTURE_ID]</pre></div><br><br>To specify a youth match:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;youth=1</pre></div><br><br>To specify an International match:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;nat=1</pre></div><br><br>To specify an Under 20 match:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;u20=1</pre></div><br><br>If the match is not found, you will receive the applicable error message.<br><br><b>Response</b><br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&lt;livescoring&gt;
  &lt;match_has_started&gt;1&lt;/match_has_started&gt;
  &lt;match_has_finished&gt;1&lt;/match_has_finished&gt;
  &lt;homescore&gt;21&lt;/homescore&gt;
  &lt;guestscore&gt;21&lt;/guestscore&gt;
  &lt;gametime&gt;4937&lt;/gametime&gt;
&lt;/livescoring&gt;</pre></div><br><br><b>Notes:</b><br><br><b>Match Started/Finished</b> 1 if true, 0 if false.<br><br><b>Game Time</b> Number of seconds on the game clock. Starts at 0 in the first half, and 40x60 in the second half.<br><br><b>Before match</b> The scores will always be 0 before a match.<br><br><b>Delays</b> Sometimes a match may be delayed. In which case the scores will be 0, and "match_has_started" will be false, until the match is run.</div>                                                  </div>
                                                </div>
                                                                                            
                                                <div>
                                                  <div>
