                                                  </div>
                                                  <div id="answer470" style="padding:5px; display:none;">
                                                    <div><b>Request</b><br>To tell the API that this is a request for one or more match summaries:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;r=ms</pre></div><br><br><b>Additional Request Data</b><br>At least one of the following is required:<br><br>To retrieve a single match summary:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;fixtureid=[FIXTURE_ID]</pre></div><br><br>To retrieve multiple match summaries:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;fixtureids=[FIXTURE_ID],[FIXTURE_ID]</pre></div><br><br>To retrieve a match summary for a youth match:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;fixtureid=[FIXTURE_ID]&amp;youth=1</pre></div><br><br>To retrieve a match summary for an International match:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;fixtureid=[FIXTURE_ID]&amp;nat=1</pre></div><br><br>To retrieve a match summary for an Under 20 match:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;fixtureid=[FIXTURE_ID]&amp;u20=1</pre></div><br><br>If any report is not found, no information will be returned for that report, not even an empty element.<br><br><b>Response</b><br><br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&lt;match_summary fixtureid="967"&gt;
