                                                <div>
                                                  <div>
                                                    <a href="javascript: expand(document.getElementById('answer462'));">
                                                      Members                                                    </a>
                                                  </div>
                                                  <div id="answer462" style="padding:5px; display:none;">
                                                    <div><b>Request</b><br>To tell the API that this is a request for member information:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;r=m</pre></div><br><br><b>Additional Request Data</b><br>At least one of the following is required:<br><br>To retrieve an individual member:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;memberid=[MEMBER_ID]</pre></div><br><br>To retrieve a group of members:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;memberids=[MEMBER_ID],[MEMBER_ID],...</pre></div><br><br>Each of the above can be requested at the same time.<br><br>If any member is not found, no information will be returned for that member, not even an empty member element.<br><br><b>Response</b><br>If a valid member key is not supplied, or the requesting member is not the owner of the member information, the following items are returned:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&lt;member id="1"&gt;
  &lt;id&gt;1&lt;/id&gt;
  &lt;username&gt;Northern_Knight&lt;/username&gt;
  &lt;teamid&gt;1&lt;/teamid&gt;
  &lt;active&gt;1&lt;/active&gt;
  &lt;lastclick&gt;1266526166&lt;/lastclick&gt;
  &lt;dateregistered&gt;1147007591&lt;/dateregistered&gt;
&lt;/member&gt;</pre></div><br><br>If a valid member key is given, and requesting member is the owner of the member information, the following items are returned:<br><br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&lt;member id="2"&gt;
  &lt;id&gt;2&lt;/id&gt;
  &lt;username&gt;Jeremy&lt;/username&gt;
  &lt;realname&gt;Jeremy&lt;/realname&gt;
  &lt;email&gt;someone@somewhere.com&lt;/email&gt;
  &lt;memberlevel&gt;7&lt;/memberlevel&gt;
  &lt;teamid&gt;2&lt;/teamid&gt;
  &lt;cash&gt;0.00&lt;/cash&gt;
  &lt;active&gt;1&lt;/active&gt;
  &lt;lastclick&gt;1266573457&lt;/lastclick&gt;
  &lt;dateregistered&gt;1147007678&lt;/dateregistered&gt;
&lt;/member&gt;</pre></div><br><br><b>Notes:</b><br><br><b>Member level</b> The security level of the member. The available levels are:<br><b>1</b> Unverified<br><b>2</b> Suspended<br><b>3</b> Free member<br><b>4</b> Premium member<br><b>5</b> Forum moderator<br><b>6</b> Game master<br><b>7</b> Developer<br><br><b>Cash</b> The member's cash balance, in BR dollars.<br><br><b>Active</b> Indicates whether or not this is an active member, currently owning a club.<br><br><b>Last click</b> (Timestamp BRT) - The date of the member's last click.<br><br><b>Date registered</b> (Timestamp BRT) - The date when the member registered for the game.</div>                                                  </div>
                                                </div>
                                                                                            
                                                <div>
                                                  <div>
                                                    <a href="javascript: expand(document.getElementById('answer478'));">
                                                      Player History                                                    </a>
                                                  </div>
                                                  <div id="answer478" style="padding:5px; display:none;">
                                                    <div><b>Request</b><br>To tell the API that this is a request for player history information:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;r=ph</pre></div><br><br><b>Additional Request Data</b><br><br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;playerid=[PLAYER_ID]</pre></div><br><br>If no player history is available, no information will be returned, not even an empty element.<br><br><b>Response</b><br><br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&lt;entry id="15877146"&gt;
  &lt;playerid&gt;2306136&lt;/playerid&gt;
  &lt;event&gt;
    Injured during match (&lt;a href="tools.live.scoring.php#fixture
      =5201142"&gt;5201142&lt;/a&gt;). Will recover for next match.
  &lt;/event&gt;
  &lt;date&gt;1276075433&lt;/date&gt;
&lt;/entry&gt;
&lt;entry id="15399013"&gt;
  &lt;playerid&gt;2306136&lt;/playerid&gt;
  &lt;event&gt;
    Speed popped from &lt;rank value=8 /&gt; to &lt;rank value=9 /&gt;.
  &lt;/event&gt;
  &lt;date&gt;1273292153&lt;/date&gt;
&lt;/entry&gt;
...</pre></div><br><br><b>Notes:</b><br><br><b>Date</b> (Timestamp BRT) - The date of the event.<br><br><b>Tags</b> - Teams, Players, Members, and Skill Ranking Levels are provided as tags, e.g. <team id="1">, <natteam id="1">, <u20team id="1">, <player id="1">, <youthplayer id="1">, <member id="1">, <rank value="5"><br><br><b>Pops</b> - Pops are hidden for 7 days for free members. Pops are provided as normal for premium members.</rank></member></youthplayer></player></u20team></natteam></team></div>                                                  </div>
                                                </div>
                                                                                            
                                                <div>
                                                  <div>
                                                    <a href="javascript: expand(document.getElementById('answer460'));">
                                                      Players                                                    </a>
                                                  </div>
                                                  <div id="answer460" style="padding: 5px; display: block;">
                                                    <div><b>Request</b><br>To tell the API that this is a request for player information:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;r=p</pre></div><br><br><b>Additional Request Data</b><br>At least one of the following is required:<br><br>To retrieve an individual player:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;playerid=[PLAYER_ID]</pre></div><br><br>To retrieve a group of players:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;playerids=[PLAYER_ID],[PLAYER_ID],...</pre></div><br><br>To retrieve all players from a team:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;teamid=[TEAM_ID]</pre></div><br><br>All of the above can be requested at the same time.<br><br>If any player is not found, no information will be returned for that player, not even an empty player element.<br><br><b>Response</b><br>If a valid member key is not supplied, or the member is not the owner of the player, the following items are returned:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&lt;player id="2306148"&gt;
&lt;id&gt;2306148&lt;/id&gt;
  &lt;teamid&gt;2&lt;/teamid&gt;
  &lt;fname&gt;Rongo&lt;/fname&gt;
  &lt;lname&gt;Tribe&lt;/lname&gt;
  &lt;birthday&gt;06:5&lt;/birthday&gt;
  &lt;age&gt;30&lt;/age&gt;
  &lt;hand&gt;Right&lt;/hand&gt;
  &lt;foot&gt;Left&lt;/foot&gt;
  &lt;nationality&gt;NZ&lt;/nationality&gt;
  &lt;csr&gt;6464&lt;/csr&gt;
  &lt;salary&gt;41383&lt;/salary&gt;
  &lt;form&gt;8&lt;/form&gt;
  &lt;aggression&gt;5&lt;/aggression&gt;
  &lt;discipline&gt;2&lt;/discipline&gt;
  &lt;energy&gt;7&lt;/energy&gt;
  &lt;leadership&gt;1&lt;/leadership&gt;
  &lt;experience&gt;1&lt;/experience&gt;
  &lt;weight&gt;88&lt;/weight&gt;
  &lt;height&gt;182&lt;/height&gt;
  &lt;injured&gt;0&lt;/injured&gt;
  &lt;youthid&gt;0&lt;/youthid&gt;
  &lt;jersey&gt;255&lt;/jersey&gt;
  &lt;joined&gt;1197590177&lt;/joined&gt;
&lt;/player&gt;</pre></div><br><br>If a valid member key is given, and member is the owner of the player, the following items are returned:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&lt;player id="2306148"&gt;
&lt;id&gt;2306148&lt;/id&gt;
  &lt;teamid&gt;2&lt;/teamid&gt;
  &lt;fname&gt;Rongo&lt;/fname&gt;
  &lt;lname&gt;Tribe&lt;/lname&gt;
  &lt;birthday&gt;06:5&lt;/birthday&gt;
  &lt;age&gt;30&lt;/age&gt;
  &lt;hand&gt;Right&lt;/hand&gt;
  &lt;foot&gt;Left&lt;/foot&gt;
  &lt;nationality&gt;NZ&lt;/nationality&gt;
  &lt;csr&gt;6464&lt;/csr&gt;
  &lt;salary&gt;41383&lt;/salary&gt;
  &lt;stamina&gt;6&lt;/stamina&gt;
  &lt;handling&gt;7&lt;/handling&gt;
  &lt;attack&gt;8&lt;/attack&gt;
  &lt;defense&gt;1&lt;/defense&gt;
  &lt;technique&gt;2&lt;/technique&gt;
  &lt;strength&gt;3&lt;/strength&gt;
  &lt;jumping&gt;3&lt;/jumping&gt;
  &lt;speed&gt;7&lt;/speed&gt;
  &lt;agility&gt;7&lt;/agility&gt;
  &lt;kicking&gt;4&lt;/kicking&gt;
  &lt;form&gt;8&lt;/form&gt;
  &lt;aggression&gt;5&lt;/aggression&gt;
  &lt;discipline&gt;2&lt;/discipline&gt;
  &lt;energy&gt;7&lt;/energy&gt;
  &lt;leadership&gt;1&lt;/leadership&gt;
  &lt;experience&gt;1&lt;/experience&gt;
  &lt;weight&gt;88&lt;/weight&gt;
  &lt;height&gt;182&lt;/height&gt;
  &lt;injured&gt;0&lt;/injured&gt;
  &lt;contract&gt;0&lt;/contract&gt;
  &lt;youthid&gt;0&lt;/youthid&gt;
  &lt;jersey&gt;255&lt;/jersey&gt;
  &lt;joined&gt;1197590177&lt;/joined&gt;
  &lt;pops&gt;
    &lt;skill&gt;stamina&lt;/skill&gt;
    &lt;skill&gt;attack&lt;/skill&gt;
  &lt;/pops&gt;
&lt;/player&gt;</pre></div><br><br><b>Notes:</b><br><br><b>Injured</b> (Timestamp BRT) - If this date is greater than the current Blackout Rugby Time, the player is currently injured.<br><br><b>Youth ID</b> - If this value is set (not equal to 0), it represents the player's ID when they were a youth player.<br><br><b>Joined</b> (Timestamp BRT) - The date in Blackout Rugby Time when the player joined their current squad.<br><br><b>Contract</b> (Timestamp BRT) - If this value is set (not equal to 0), and the date is greater than the current Blackout Rugby Time, the player is under contract.<br><br><b>Jersey</b> - If this value is set (not equal to 255), this represents the jersey number given to the player by the manager.<br><br><b>Pops</b> - The pops element holds any skills which have recently "popped". These are provided for premium managers only.<br><br><b>Energy %</b> - If the player is owned by a premium manager, the energy percentage out of 110% is provided. If not, the normal value from 1-11 is provided.<br><br><b>Birthday</b> - The player's birthday is provided in the format, <b>WW:D</b>. WW = week with a leading 0 for weeks less than 10, and D = day. <br><br><b>Youth Players</b><br><br>To retrieve a youth player:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;playerid=[PLAYER_ID]&amp;youth=1</pre></div><br><br>If a valid member key is given, and member is the owner of the player, the following items are returned:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&lt;player id="4356278"&gt;
  &lt;id&gt;4356278&lt;/id&gt;
  &lt;teamid&gt;2&lt;/teamid&gt;
  &lt;fname&gt;Arenui&lt;/fname&gt;
  &lt;lname&gt;Laulala&lt;/lname&gt;
  &lt;birthday&gt;06:5&lt;/birthday&gt;
  &lt;age&gt;18&lt;/age&gt;
  &lt;hand&gt;Right&lt;/hand&gt;
  &lt;foot&gt;Right&lt;/foot&gt;
  &lt;nationality&gt;NZ&lt;/nationality&gt;
  &lt;csr&gt;20008&lt;/csr&gt;
  &lt;salary&gt;82897&lt;/salary&gt;
  &lt;stamina&gt;Unknown&lt;/stamina&gt;
  &lt;handling&gt;Medium&lt;/handling&gt;
  &lt;attack&gt;Unknown&lt;/attack&gt;
  &lt;defense&gt;Unknown&lt;/defense&gt;
  &lt;technique&gt;Unknown&lt;/technique&gt;
  &lt;strength&gt;Unknown&lt;/strength&gt;
  &lt;jumping&gt;Unknown&lt;/jumping&gt;
  &lt;speed&gt;Unknown&lt;/speed&gt;
  &lt;agility&gt;Unknown&lt;/agility&gt;
  &lt;kicking&gt;Low&lt;/kicking&gt;
  &lt;form&gt;7&lt;/form&gt;
  &lt;aggression&gt;2&lt;/aggression&gt;
  &lt;discipline&gt;4&lt;/discipline&gt;
  &lt;energy&gt;11&lt;/energy&gt;
  &lt;leadership&gt;2&lt;/leadership&gt;
  &lt;experience&gt;2&lt;/experience&gt;
  &lt;weight&gt;93&lt;/weight&gt;
  &lt;height&gt;199&lt;/height&gt;
  &lt;jersey&gt;255&lt;/jersey&gt;
  &lt;scouted&gt;1257990490&lt;/scouted&gt;
  &lt;pops&gt;&lt;/pops&gt;
  &lt;reveals&gt;
    &lt;skill&gt;handling&lt;/skill&gt;
  &lt;/reveals&gt;
&lt;/player&gt;</pre></div><br><br><b>Notes:</b><br><br>Youth players do not have contract dates, joined dates, or injured dates, but they have a scouted date which represents the date they were introduced into the youth squad. All normally hidden values on the main site are also hidden in the API, such as skills and CSR.<br><br><b>Skills revealed</b> - Providing the owning member is making the call, if a skill has not been revealed, it will be returned as "Unknown". If a skill has been semi-revealed, it is returned as one of "Low", "Medium", or "High". If a skill is completely revealed, it will be returned as normal (an integer).<br><br><b>Reveals</b> - The reveals element holds any skills recently revealed for premium managers only. These represent the blue ribbons provided on the main site.<br><br><b>Scouting stars</b> - If the member key is provided, and the member is premium, the number of stars used to the scout the player will be provided if available, under the key "scouting_stars_used".<br><br><b>National and Under 20 Players</b><br><br>To retrieve a National player:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;playerid=[PLAYER_ID]&amp;nat=1</pre></div><br><br>To retrieve all players from a National team:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;teamid=[TEAM_ID]&amp;nat=1</pre></div><br><br>To retrieve an Under 20 player:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;playerid=[PLAYER_ID]&amp;u20=1</pre></div><br><br>To retrieve all players from an Under 20 team:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;teamid=[TEAM_ID]&amp;u20=1</pre></div><br><br><b>Notes:</b><br><br>Retrieving a National or U20 player will return all of the same information as the club player except for energy, injured, joined, and jersey which represent the player as part of their National or U20 team. National\U20 managers can see all skills for players in their national side.<br><br><b>Players for sale</b><br><br>Players who are currently for sale on the transfer market will show all skills and their levels.<br><br>As well as the skill levels, the following information related to the transfer is made available:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&lt;forsale&gt;1&lt;/forsale&gt;
&lt;listed&gt;1276780714&lt;/listed&gt;
&lt;deadline&gt;1277039880&lt;/deadline&gt;
&lt;asking&gt;2000000&lt;/asking&gt;
&lt;price&gt;2486747&lt;/price&gt;
&lt;bidteamid&gt;65&lt;/bidteamid&gt;</pre></div><br><br><b>Notes:</b><br><br><b>Listed</b> (Timestamp BRT) - The date in Blackout Rugby Time when the player was placed on the transfer market.<br><br><b>Deadline</b> (Timestamp BRT) - The date in Blackout Rugby Time when the player will be transferred to the highest bidder.<br><br><b>Bidteamid</b> - The ID of the team currently leading the auction. If there are no bids, this tag will be empty.</div>                                                  </div>
                                                </div>
                                                                                            
                                                <div>
                                                  <div>
                                                    <a href="javascript: expand(document.getElementById('answer471'));">
                                                      Player Statistics                                                    </a>
                                                  </div>
                                                  <div id="answer471" style="padding: 5px; display: block;">
                                                    <div><b>Request</b><br>To tell the API that this is a request for player statistics:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;r=ps</pre></div><br><br><b>Additional Request Data</b><br>At least one of the following is required:<br><br>To retrieve an individual player's statistics:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;playerid=[PLAYER_ID]</pre></div><br><br>To retrieve a group of players' statistics:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;playerids=[PLAYER_ID],[PLAYER_ID],...</pre></div><br><br>To retrieve league statistics:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;playerid=[PLAYER_ID]&amp;league=1 (Current season)
or
&amp;playerid=[PLAYER_ID]&amp;league=1&amp;season=[SEASON]</pre></div><br><br>To retrieve National player statistics:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;playerid=[PLAYER_ID]&amp;nat=1 (Current season)
or
&amp;playerid=[PLAYER_ID]&amp;nat=1&amp;season=[SEASON]</pre></div><br><br>To retrieve World Cup player statistics:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;playerid=[PLAYER_ID]&amp;nat=1&amp;wc=1 (Current season)
or
