                                                  <div>
                                                    <a href="javascript: expand(document.getElementById('answer477'));">
                                                      Ranking History                                                    </a>
                                                  </div>
                                                  <div id="answer477" style="padding:5px; display:none;">
                                                    <div><b>Premium</b><br>This feature will only work when the owner of the club is a premium member, and their member key is provided, unless the history for a National/U20 side is being requested in which case, the member must simply be a premium member, and does not have to be the current National/U20 manager.<br><br><b>Request</b><br>To tell the API that this is a request for ranking history information:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;r=rkh</pre></div><br><br><b>Additional Request Data</b><br><br>To retrieve normal club rankings history:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;teamid=[TEAM_ID]</pre></div><br><br>To retrieve International rankings history:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;nat=1&amp;iso=[COUNTRY_ISO]</pre></div><br><br>To retrieve Under 20 rankings history:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;u20=1&amp;iso=[COUNTRY_ISO]</pre></div><br><br>If no rankings history is available, no information will be returned, not even an empty element.<br><br><b>Response</b><br><br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&lt;ranking id="104936"&gt;
