                                                  <div>
                                                    <a href="javascript: expand(document.getElementById('answer468'));">
                                                      Standings                                                    </a>
                                                  </div>
                                                  <div id="answer468" style="padding:5px; display:none;">
                                                    <div><b>Request</b><br>To tell the API that this is a request for standings information:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;r=s</pre></div><br><br><b>Additional Request Data</b><br>At least one of the following is required:<br><br>To retrieve standings for a senior league:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;leagueid=[LEAGUE_ID]</pre></div><br><br>To retrieve standings for a youth league:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;leagueid=[LEAGUE_ID]&amp;youth=1</pre></div><br><br>To retrieve International standings for the current season:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;nat=1</pre></div><br><br>To retrieve Under 20 standings for the current season:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;u20=1</pre></div><br><br>For International &amp; Under 20 standings, a season can be specified:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">nat=1&amp;season=[SEASON]
or
u20=1&amp;season=[SEASON]</pre></div><br><br>If any standings information is not found, no information will be returned for that standing, not even an empty element.<br><br><b>Response</b><br><br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&lt;standing id="44"&gt;
  &lt;id&gt;44&lt;/id&gt;
  &lt;country_iso&gt;NZ&lt;/country_iso&gt;
