                                                    <a href="javascript: expand(document.getElementById('answer479'));">
                                                      Team History                                                    </a>
                                                  </div>
                                                  <div id="answer479" style="padding:5px; display:none;">
                                                    <div><b>Request</b><br>To tell the API that this is a request for team history information:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;r=th</pre></div><br><br><b>Additional Request Data</b><br><br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;teamid=[TEAM_ID]</pre></div><br><br>If no team history is available, no information will be returned, not even an empty element.<br><br><b>Response</b><br><br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&lt;entry id="741620"&gt;
  &lt;teamid&gt;2&lt;/teamid&gt;
  &lt;event&gt;
    Shifted to league &lt;a href="club.league.php?id=69384"&gt;V.97&lt;/a&gt;
      as part of season 9 bot flush.
  &lt;/event&gt;
  &lt;date&gt;1275192138&lt;/date&gt;
&lt;/entry&gt;
&lt;entry id="682167"&gt;
  &lt;teamid&gt;2&lt;/teamid&gt;
  &lt;event&gt;
    Sold &lt;player id=2306134 /&gt; to &lt;team id=9879 /&gt; for $24,501.
  &lt;/event&gt;
  &lt;date&gt;1266531007&lt;/date&gt;
&lt;/entry&gt;
&lt;entry id="667945"&gt;
  &lt;teamid&gt;2&lt;/teamid&gt;
  &lt;event&gt;
    Relegated to league &lt;a href="club.league.php?id=61808"&gt;V.190&lt;/a&gt;
      after season 7.
  &lt;/event&gt;
  &lt;date&gt;1265435202&lt;/date&gt;
&lt;/entry&gt;
...</pre></div><br><br><b>Notes:</b><br><br><b>Date</b> (Timestamp BRT) - The date of the event.<br><br><b>Tags</b> - Teams, Players, Members, and Skill Ranking Levels are provided as tags, e.g. <team id="1">, <natteam id="1">, <u20team id="1">, <player id="1">, <youthplayer id="1">, <member id="1">, <rank value="5"></rank></member></youthplayer></player></u20team></natteam></team></div>                                                  </div>
