                                                    <a href="javascript: expand(document.getElementById('answer461'));">
                                                      Teams                                                    </a>
                                                  </div>
                                                  <div id="answer461" style="padding: 5px; display: block;">
                                                    <div><b>Request</b><br>To tell the API that this is a request for team information:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;r=t</pre></div><br><br><b>Additional Request Data</b><br>At least one of the following is required:<br><br>To retrieve an individual team:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;teamid=[TEAM_ID]</pre></div><br><br>To retrieve a group of teams:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;teamids=[TEAM_ID],[TEAM_ID],...</pre></div><br><br>Each of the above can be requested at the same time.<br><br>To retrieve all teams within a region:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;regionid=[REGION_ID]</pre></div><br><br>To retrieve all teams within a league:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;leagueid=[LEAGUE_ID]</pre></div><br><br>If any team is not found, no information will be returned for that team, not even an empty team element.<br><br><b>Response</b><br>If a valid member key is not supplied, or the member is not the owner of the team, the following items are returned:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&lt;team id="1"&gt;
  &lt;id&gt;1&lt;/id&gt;
  &lt;name&gt;Northern+Knights&lt;/name&gt;
  &lt;country_iso&gt;NZ&lt;/country&gt;
  &lt;region&gt;2&lt;/region&gt;
  &lt;stadium&gt;Blackoutrugby.com+Park&lt;/stadium&gt;
  &lt;bot&gt;0&lt;/bot&gt;
  &lt;nickname_1&gt;Knights&lt;/nickname_1&gt;
  &lt;nickname_2/&gt;
  &lt;nickname_3/&gt;
  &lt;ranking_points&gt;62.711&lt;/ranking_points&gt;
  &lt;regional_rank&gt;12&lt;/regional_rank&gt;
  &lt;national_rank&gt;110&lt;/national_rank&gt;
  &lt;world_rank&gt;756&lt;/world_rank&gt;
  &lt;prev_ranking_points&gt;62.711&lt;/prev_ranking_points&gt;
  &lt;prev_regional_rank&gt;12&lt;/prev_regional_rank&gt;
  &lt;prev_national_rank&gt;109&lt;/prev_national_rank&gt;
  &lt;prev_world_rank&gt;756&lt;/prev_world_rank&gt;
  &lt;leagueid&gt;123&lt;/leagueid&gt;
  &lt;manager&gt;2&lt;/manager&gt;
&lt;/team&gt;</pre></div><br><br>If a valid member key is given, and member is the owner of the team, the following items are returned:<br><br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&lt;team id="2"&gt;
  &lt;id&gt;2&lt;/id&gt;
  &lt;name&gt;Chiefs&lt;/name&gt;
  &lt;country_iso&gt;NZ&lt;/country&gt;
  &lt;region&gt;2&lt;/region&gt;
  &lt;stadium&gt;Blackout+Rugby+Stadium&lt;/stadium&gt;
  &lt;drift&gt;#&lt;/drift&gt;
  &lt;rush&gt;#&lt;/rush&gt;
  &lt;manonman&gt;#&lt;/manonman&gt;
  &lt;bot&gt;0&lt;/bot&gt;
  &lt;contentment&gt;#&lt;/contentment&gt;
  &lt;members&gt;####&lt;/members&gt;
  &lt;stadium_capacity&gt;####&lt;/stadium_capacity&gt;
  &lt;stadium_standing&gt;####&lt;/stadium_standing&gt;
  &lt;stadium_uncovered&gt;####&lt;/stadium_uncovered&gt;
