  &lt;stadium_members&gt;###&lt;/stadium_members&gt;
  &lt;stadium_corporate&gt;###&lt;/stadium_corporate&gt;
  &lt;bank_balance&gt;######&lt;/bank_balance&gt;
  &lt;nickname_1/&gt;
  &lt;nickname_2/&gt;
  &lt;nickname_3/&gt;
  &lt;ltnt_effectiveness&gt;100&lt;/ltnt_effectiveness&gt;
  &lt;ltnt_effectiveness_youth&gt;100&lt;/ltnt_effectiveness_youth&gt;
  &lt;ranking_points&gt;46.528&lt;/ranking_points&gt;
  &lt;regional_rank&gt;33&lt;/regional_rank&gt;
  &lt;national_rank&gt;327&lt;/national_rank&gt;
  &lt;world_rank&gt;2579&lt;/world_rank&gt;
  &lt;major_sponsor&gt;5&lt;/major_sponsor&gt;
  &lt;minor_sponsors&gt;7&lt;/minor_sponsors&gt;
  &lt;prev_ranking_points&gt;46.528&lt;/prev_ranking_points&gt;
  &lt;prev_regional_rank&gt;34&lt;/prev_regional_rank&gt;
  &lt;prev_national_rank&gt;329&lt;/prev_national_rank&gt;
  &lt;prev_world_rank&gt;2585&lt;/prev_world_rank&gt;
  &lt;leagueid&gt;123&lt;/leagueid&gt;
  &lt;scouting_stars&gt;5&lt;/scouting_stars&gt;
  &lt;manager&gt;2&lt;/manager&gt;
&lt;/team&gt;</pre></div><br><br><b>Notes:</b><br><br><b>Previous Rankings</b> The previous ranking points and positions are provided to show the difference between the rankings before the last match, and the current rankings.<br><br><b>Bots</b> Bot teams will not return a manager tag.<br><br><b>National and Under 20 Teams</b><br><br>To retrieve a National team:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;teamid=[TEAM_ID]&amp;nat=1</pre></div><br>or <div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;country=[COUNTRY_ISO]&amp;nat=1</pre></div><br><br>To retrieve an Under 20 team:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;teamid=[TEAM_ID]&amp;u20=1</pre></div><br>or <div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&amp;country=[COUNTRY_ISO]&amp;u20=1</pre></div><br><br>Multiple team IDs, and\or country ISO's are supported.<br><br>If a valid member key is not supplied, or the member is not the manager of the National\U20 team, the following items are returned:<br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&lt;team id="9"&gt;
