  &lt;prev_ranking_points&gt;90.1881&lt;/prev_ranking_points&gt;
  &lt;prev_world_rank&gt;3&lt;/prev_world_rank&gt;
  &lt;nat&gt;1&lt;/nat&gt;
  &lt;manager&gt;608&lt;/manager&gt;
&lt;/team&gt;</pre></div><br><br>If a valid member key is given, and member is the manager of the National\U20 team, the following items are returned:<br><br><div class="code"><pre style="margin:0; padding:0;">&lt;team id="2"&gt;
  &lt;id&gt;2&lt;/id&gt;
