  &lt;nickname_2/&gt;
  &lt;nickname_3/&gt;
  &lt;ltnt_effectiveness&gt;100&lt;/ltnt_effectiveness&gt;
  &lt;ranking_points&gt;69.7074&lt;/ranking_points&gt;
  &lt;world_rank&gt;15&lt;/world_rank&gt;
  &lt;prev_ranking_points&gt;70.8777&lt;/prev_ranking_points&gt;
  &lt;prev_world_rank&gt;14&lt;/prev_world_rank&gt;
  &lt;nat&gt;1&lt;/nat&gt;
  &lt;manager&gt;12324&lt;/manager&gt;
&lt;/team&gt;</pre></div><br><br><b>Notes:</b><br><br><b>National\U20 Manager</b> The ID of the current National\U20 manager is provided in the <manager> tag.</manager></div>                                                  </div>
                                                </div>
                                                                                            
